com.sun.jdi

Interface VoidType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Mirror, Type

    @Exported
public interface VoidType
extends Type
    The type of all primitive void values accessed in the target VM. Calls to Value.type() will return an implementor of this interface.

    1.3
